To change the theme of the launcher and make the background completely transparent, pursue the following steps:
1 make a backup of the following files:
'/usr/share/unity/icons/launcher_icon_back_54.svg'
'/usr/share/unity/icons/launcher_icon_edge_54.svg'
'/usr/share/unity/icons/launcher_icon_glow_62.svg'
'/usr/share/unity/icons/launcher_icon_shadow_62.svg'
'/usr/share/unity/icons/launcher_icon_shine_54.svg'

2 Replace the originals with the files included here

3 Restart your system
